16:46.731 --> 16:48.064
you're asking me
personal questions.

16:48.233 --> 16:49.732
I didn't invite you,
and we barely know each other.

16:49.751 --> 16:52.176
Well, that's mean,
but I have two teenage girls,

16:52.369 --> 16:54.512
so you got nothing on them.

16:54.663 --> 16:56.255
Something's up, Paula,

16:56.391 --> 17:00.167
and I think that that something
has to do with your health.

17:00.261 --> 17:04.747
I've been through this with--
with people before.

17:04.840 --> 17:06.098
Drinking in the morning,

17:06.251 --> 17:07.250
pushing people away--
you know, really, honestly,

17:07.268 --> 17:08.526
