for me,

17:08.695 --> 17:13.322
so I would like you
to tell me please what's wrong.

17:14.776 --> 17:16.275
Dance for it.

17:16.369 --> 17:18.778
-What?
-This is my favorite song.

17:18.930 --> 17:20.854
Dance on the bar,
and I'll tell you.

17:20.874 --> 17:22.356
Maybe.

