18:25.330 --> 18:27.012
They want to run a biopsy
and a couple of tests,

18:27.107 --> 18:28.088
and I thought,
"You know what sounds better?

18:28.108 --> 18:29.607
A drink," so cheers.

18:29.758 --> 18:30.850
Paula, I am so sorry,

18:31.018 --> 18:32.944
but I gotta tell you
that I think that you should

18:33.095 --> 18:35.004
go get those tests,
like, right now.

18:35.097 --> 18:37.173
