who has been bugging me

18:44.124 --> 18:47.199
to take her shopping
for a homecoming dress,

18:47.352 --> 18:49.034
but this is not important.

18:49.129 --> 18:52.112
That's what I want to do.

18:52.132 --> 18:52.964
