<i> -♪ Answer my prayer, babe </i>

19:14.879 --> 19:16.803
<i> ♪ Answer my prayer </i>

19:16.823 --> 19:19.198
(phone buzzing)

19:21.219 --> 19:23.569
-Who is calling you so much?
